data.description: Serenity by the river, enjoy your own 60ft of riverfront property, fully landscaped with Extra parking! Gourmet Kitchen with Granite counter tops & lots of cabinet space, living room with a cozy pellet stove and Large family room with two separate french doors that enter onto a Huge entertaining deck, this Home shows very well. Brand new Elementary being build just down the road. It feels like a home away from home, this is a Must See.
